                            joined the company of <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/74">John
                                of Ephesus</persName> at <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/399">the Monastery of Yoḥannan
                                Urṭaya</placeName> and lived there for about twenty years until his
                            death. </desc>
                    </event>
                </listEvent>
